In order to differentiate types of notifications, so that blog notifications do not look the same as page notifications, it would be helpful to be able to set a custom email subject format for each type of notification.

This is currently only possible by doing something like what is described in [this Answers comment|https://answers.atlassian.com/questions/61466/is-it-possible-to-change-the-subject-of-notification-emails-sent-from-confluence], which involves modifying the source code.

