*Problem:*
Space Directory doesn't show the list of Spaces.

*Symptoms details:*
* Address http://site/wiki/spacedirectory/view.action will display an empty page with the top and sidebar but no list of Spaces.
* Space Directory, All Spaces, Site Spaces, Personal Spaces, Favourite Spaces, Archived Spaces and all Categories will display an empty page.
